# === 项目特定：敏感文件 ===
# 用户配置文件（包含个人路径、邮箱、授权码）
scripts/config.py
/scripts/*.py
/scripts/VERSION
/scripts/CHANGELOG.md
/scripts/config_template.py
交付包/*/scripts/config.py
源文件/*/scripts/config.py
